## Typography

### Font Family

- **Primary**: SF Pro Display (system default)
- **Monospace**: SF Mono for code/addresses

### Type Scale

| Style      | Size | Weight         | Letter Spacing | Line Height |
| ---------- | ---- | -------------- | -------------- | ----------- |
| Display    | 36pt | Bold (700)     | -0.5pt         | 1.1         |
| Headline   | 28pt | Bold (700)     | -0.4pt         | 1.2         |
| Title      | 22pt | Semibold (600) | -0.3pt         | 1.25        |
| Body Large | 18pt | Regular (400)  | 0pt            | 1.5         |
| Body       | 16pt | Regular (400)  | 0pt            | 1.5         |
| Caption    | 14pt | Regular (400)  | 0pt            | 1.4         |
| Small      | 12pt | Medium (500)   | 0.2pt          | 1.3         |

### Typography Rules

- Headlines use **tight letter-spacing** for impact
- Body text uses **normal spacing** for readability
- Button text uses **semibold weight** with slight tracking
- Always ensure sufficient contrast (WCAG AA minimum)

