## Component Guidelines

### Buttons (PButton)

#### Primary Button

- Background: `primary` (#1DA1F2)
- Text: `primaryForeground` (white)
- Radius: `full` (pill-shaped)
- Min Height: 52pt for touch targets
- Font: Semibold, 16-17pt
- Shadow: `sm` at rest, `md` on press
- Animation: 0.97 scale on press with spring

#### Secondary Button

- Background: `card` (white/dark surface)
- Border: 1pt `border` color
- Text: `foreground`
- Radius: `full`
- Same sizing as primary

#### Ghost Button

- Background: transparent
- Text: `foreground`
- On hover: subtle background tint
- No border

#### Destructive Button

- Background: `destructive`
- Text: `destructiveForeground`
- Use sparingly for critical actions

### Cards (PCard)

- Background: `card`
- Radius: `xl` (20pt)
- Shadow: `sm` at rest
- Padding: `md` (16pt) internal
- Border: optional 1pt `border` for emphasis

### Text Fields (PTextField)

- Background: `muted` or `card`
- Border: 1pt `input` color
- Radius: `lg` (14pt)
- Height: 48-52pt
- Padding: `md` horizontal
- Focus: 2pt `ring` color border
- Placeholder: `mutedForeground`

### Tooltips (PTooltip)

- Background: `foreground` (inverted)
- Text: `background` (inverted)
- Radius: `md` (10pt)
- Shadow: `md`
- Arrow: subtle, matching background
- Animation: fade + slight scale from 0.95

