## Accessibility

### Color Contrast

- All text must meet WCAG AA standards (4.5:1 for body, 3:1 for large text)
- Interactive elements need visible focus indicators
- Don't rely on color alone to convey meaning

### Touch Targets

- Minimum 44x44pt touch targets on iOS
- Buttons should have generous padding
- Adequate spacing between interactive elements

### Motion

- Respect `reduceMotion` preference
- Provide non-animated alternatives
- Keep animations under 5 seconds
- Avoid rapidly flashing content

```swift
@Environment(\.accessibilityReduceMotion) var reduceMotion

// Use conditional animation
.animation(reduceMotion ? .none : .spring(response: 0.35, dampingFraction: 0.7), value: state)
```

