## Platform Considerations

### iOS

- Use SF Symbols for icons
- Support Dynamic Type for accessibility
- Implement haptic feedback for important actions
- Follow iOS safe area guidelines

### macOS

- Support hover states for all interactive elements
- Implement keyboard navigation
- Use pointer cursor changes appropriately
- Support both light and dark appearances

